        "description": "Client Credentials grant: BX Finance MCP Service → PingOne API Token (Token 3).\n\nThis is NOT a token exchange — independent credential grant.\nScopes p1:read:user and p1:update:user must be enabled on the app's Resources tab (doc Part 2c).\nApp type must be Native or Web App — NOT Worker (doc Part 2c)."
      },
